summary: Adds a small house north of Morthal, next door to Jorgen\'s house.
descriptionHtml:
This mod adds a cozy little cabin north of Morthal, next door to Jorgen & Lami\'s house.  The house has a little trap door that leads to the basement.  

The house includes:

-A cooking pot
-3 Display cases
-2 Mannequins
-An enchanting table
-An alchemy table
-A bookshelf full of skill books
-A bookshelf full of spell books
-An empty bookshelf to place books on. (holds 18 books)
author: SqueakyDoggy
